videos.headline: Murray's big gain sets up a Georgia Southern TD
videos.description: Georgia Southern runs the triple option to perfection as Malik Murray gains 43 yards off the late pitch. Later in the drive, Shai Werts pounds it into the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murray's big gain sets up a Georgia Southern TD) 2020/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia Southern halts Louisiana Tech's drive with an INT
videos.description: Louisiana Tech gets the ball into the red zone, but Georgia Southern CB Justin Birdsong picks off the pass to end the drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia Southern halts Louisiana Tech's drive with an INT) 2020/12/23 ESHEET
